data.description: Nicely maintained end unit Townhome at Eagle Ridge on the  first tee of the Challenge golf course. This has a cozy front porch and a wonderful back deck to enjoy the serenity of this beautiful location.  It has a nice bright kitchen with Corian counter tops, double sink and refrigerator.  Gas fireplace in the living room with Tile wrap around. Upgraded light fixtures. Laundry room , Large Primary Bedroom with walk in closet, primary bath has a large soaking tub and walk in shower and double sinks. 2 large bedrooms upstairs with a Jack and Jill bathroom between them. Eagle Crest is home to three 18 hole golf courses, 18 hole putting course, three sports centers, a spa and miles of biking/hiking trails.
